Captain Smellyâ€™s Mechanic Guide:
Key:
PF= Plasma Falchion
GP=Gemstone Power
Psv=Passive
TG= terra guardian

Weapons:

>Plasma Falchion-Starting weapon that can get added effects upon using a gemstone on it
-Starting damage = 15 (1+ extra Damage per freindship level of tg)
-Scales off of weapon in 1st inventory slot

>Arm Blaster-Simple ranged weapon that requires mana to use
-Starting damage- 5(+1 damage per freinship level of tg)
-is rapid fire

Gemstone Tiers-
Applies to all tiers>
Gain 1.5x damage multiplier on PF upon adding a gemstone

>Mystic Amethyst
Psv- Does Additional Magic Damage, applies Shadowflame  debuff
Gp- Blade Wave that does decent damage at the start but loses power the further it travels, travels fast, and bypasses blocks

>Sharp Topaz
Psv- High base knockback on weapon swings but slower attack speed, 
Gp- Sends sharp topaz shards that pierce threw targets but collides with blocks and applies bleeding debuff


>Energized Sapphire
Psv- Gives AttackSpeed Bonus but knock back is very low and PF damage is reduced by 15%
Gp- Sends out a energy missle that explodes on contact and applies electrified debuff

>Bloody Ruby
Psv-Gives lifedrain on sword swings
Gp-Sends out whiplike wave that drains enemies of their hp and heals smelly for 20hp per enemy hit 

>Critical Emerald
Psv-Gives higher base crit Chance
Gp-Tornado that has high crit chance and hits multiple times for 20 damage per tick

>Shining Diamond
Psv- Has a chance to cause dazed debuff to eneimes hit by PF
GP- A quick flash that stuns enemies for 2 seconds(Cooldown 10 seconds)

Items:
Phantom device- Allows usage of phantasm blitz attack
-Can be upgraded to allow for multiple usages of phantasm blitz and reduce startup time
Tiers>
1-Can be used 1 time 
2-Can be used 2 times in quick succession
3-Can be used 3 times in quick succession
4-Can be used 4 times in quick succession
5-Can be used 5 times in quick succession and the cooldown is reduced to 7 seconds

Super moves:
Phantasm Blitz- A super quick dash attack that has a 1.5x multiplier added to whatever her current weapon damage is and grants intangibility to Smelly during attack
-Can be used 1 time per 10 seconds(7 on tier 5 of phantom device)
-Can be used multiple times in quick succession upon upgrading phantom device
